Module it.unipr.shopfx

Package it.unipr.accounts

package it.unipr.accounts
This package contains all the classes necessary to manage the main actors of this program.

The superclass Person has been implemented to provide common attributes and methods needed by its extensions. Through the concept of inheritance we have implemented the classes of User, Employee and Admin, each with developed to be used with one specific type of account only.
